history.content:
CS 88 has finally opened for enrollment with the following conditions:

There are TWO lecture sections for this class. Each is paired with a placeholder (999) lab section. Remember for classes with placeholder labs, the actual lab assignment will happen outside of the enrollment system.

If you enroll into lecture 1, you need to also enroll into lab 999A.

If you enroll into lecture 2, you need to also enroll into lab 999L.

Time conflicts will NOT be allowed - iClickers are being used in class. Even if the system allows you to enroll because the other class allows time conflicts, you are expected to attend all components of CS 88 in person and alternate exams will not be allowed.

The lecture for this class will be webcast.
